==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unmade
<hw>Un*made"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + <ets>made</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not yet made or
formed; <as>as, an <ex>unmade</ex> grave</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Properly p. p. of <ets>unmake</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Deprived of form, character, etc.; disunited.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unmagistrate</ent>⟦br⟧
